<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Точка Сбора - Оценка стажеров</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kelly+Slab&family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Profil.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="layout" style="margin-left:318px;">
    <!-- Левая панель -->
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="logo">Точка Сбора</div>
      <div class="sidebar-buttons">
        <button class="sidebar-btn active-button">Главная</button>
        <button class="sidebar-btn">Группа</button>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- Верхняя панель -->
    <header class="top-bar">
      <div class="ellipse1">
        <div class="ellipse34">
          <div class="avatar-image"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <main class="main-content">
        <div class="profile-header">
          <div class="title-container">
            <h1 class="profile-title">Стажер</h1>
            <svg class="title-underline" width="86" height="9" viewBox="0 0 86 9" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M2 6.75245C3.96459 6.64331 5.97903 4.48303 7.80756 3.7284C10.351 2.67874 12.7857 2.11328 15.5395 2.11328C17.1088 2.11328 18.6781 2.11328 20.2474 2.11328C21.3133 2.11328 23.1915 3.40564 24.0962 3.96895C27.4713 6.07043 31.3525 4.94946 35.0928 4.89678C37.4686 4.86332 39.786 4.69202 42.1374 4.58751C43.6433 4.52058 44.9821 3.65967 46.536 3.65967C47.7255 3.65967 48.0359 3.99925 49.079 4.34696C50.9924 4.98476 52.6084 5.23153 54.646 5.20606C57.6032 5.1691 60.4236 4.06834 63.3058 3.96895C64.4024 3.93113 64.765 4.40222 65.7113 4.82806C67.5502 5.65556 69.7385 5.67152 71.5188 6.75245C72.5922 7.4041 73.5822 7.39389 74.8178 7.37101C77.9723 7.31259 81.0678 6.44317 84.268 6.44317" stroke="#5D5FEF" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-info">
            <img src="wwwroot/img/image.png" alt="" class="profile-avatar">
            <span class="profile-name"></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rating-section">
          <div class="overall-rating">
            <span class="rating-label">Рейтинг</span>
            <div class="rating-bar">
              <div class="rating-fill" style="width: 96%"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="rating-value">4.8 из 5</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="section-title">Оценка по направлениям</h2>
          <div class="rating-categories">
            <div class="rating-item">
              <span class="category-label">Технические навыки</span>
              <div class="rating-bar">
                <div class="rating-fill rating-fill-1" style="width: 90%"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="rating-value">4.5 из 5</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rating-item">
              <span class="category-label">Вовлеченность</span>
              <div class="rating-bar">
                <div class="rating-fill rating-fill-2" style="width: 100%"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="rating-value">5.0 из 5</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rating-item">
              <span class="category-label">Дисциплина</span>
              <div class="rating-bar">
                <div class="rating-fill rating-fill-3" style="width: 80%"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="rating-value">4.0 из 5</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rating-item">
              <span class="category-label">Командная работа</span>
              <div class="rating-bar">
                <div class="rating-fill rating-fill-4" style="width: 96%"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="rating-value">4.8 из 5</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="section-title">Сильные стороны</h2>
          <div class="comments-section">
            <div class="comment">
              <h3>Комментарий</h3>
              <p>За 2 недели освоил React Native</p>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">
              <h3>Комментарий</h3>
              <p>По собственной инициативе доработал UX по отзывам пользователей</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
